<?php
  if (isset($_POST["prioridade"]))
    $voto = $_POST["prioridade"];
  else 
  	header("location: escolha.php");

   date_default_timezone_set('America/Sao_Paulo');
   $data = date ('d-m-Y H:i');

  $arquivo = fopen("votos.txt", "a"); // a -> append r->read w->write
  fwrite($arquivo,$data.";" .$voto."\r\n");  //escreve a opção escolhida na var $voto e quebrar a linha 
  fclose($arquivo); 


?>

It means a concept of simulation of the real world, closer to what is real. Objects are structures that carry data and behavior of
their own and can exchange messages with each other in order to form something larger, a system. This object is a representation 
of a real concept, it has states, operations (methods) and data (attributes).




